description:
Her creative pursuits extend beyond music. She is a Cannes Gold Medal-winning
voice-over artist and an actress, known for her role in the Amazon Prime
series Die Trying, created by Kenny Sebastian. Driven by a deep passion for
music's power to unite and inspire, Soundarya approaches her craft with a
holistic vision, continually evolving as an artist.
name: Soundarya: It Is What It Is Tour

performer.description: Soundarya’s music seamlessly blends modern innovation with classical elegance, creating a fresh yet timeless sound. As the youngest AUDI Q3 Youth Ambassador and runner-up on The Stage—India’s premier English singing competition on VH1 and Colors Infinity—she has made an indelible mark in the music world.
performer.name: Soundarya

description:
Known for their unique interpretations of Tom Waits' music, VKB captivates
audiences with stunning three-part harmonies and inventive arrangements. Their
performances blend global percussion, squeezeboxes, acoustic guitars, banjos,
and playful surprises like bells and whistles, creating a rich, textured
sound.  
  
Recasting Waits' characters and melodies through a feminine lens, VKB delivers
tender yet powerful renditions that honor his vision while offering a fresh,
soulful perspective.
name: Vicki Kristina Barcelona Band

performer.description: Vicki Kristina Barcelona (VKB Band) is a dynamic New York City-based trio featuring Rachelle Garniez, Amanda Homi, and Mamie Minch—acclaimed singer-songwriters with a wealth of collective experience.
performer.name: Vicki Kristina Barcelona Band
